BASISC STEPS TO DO ON GIT:
git --version 
git config --global user.name "......"
git config --global user.email "......"
mkdir projectName
cd projectName
git init

ADD YOUR FILES TO THE FOLDER AND THEN CHECK IT BY COMMAND :  ls
git status
git add FILENAME
git add --all FILESNAME

AND THE SVAE YOUR WORK BY THE COMMAND : 
git commit -m " ENTER MESSAGE THAT DISPLY WHAT THE WORK YOU DO IT "
git log 

git branch
ADD NEW BRANCH 
git branch BranchName
git checkout BranchName
git checkout -b BranchName
git merge BranchName
git checkout -d BranchName








